INSERT INTO `main_table` VALUES ('1243', 'Short Stories', '', '', '', '', 'Elizabeth Warnock Fernea', '', '', '', 'Women and the Family in the Middle East', '', '', '', '', 'University of Texas Press', 'Austin, U.S.A.', '1985', 'Preface -- Poem / Salma Khadra Jayyusi -- Part I. Introduction: Algerian women discuss the need for change / Fatiha Akeb and Malika Abdelaziz -- Part II. The Family: The Arab family and the challenge of social transformation -- The charm / Ilfat Ildibi -- New images, old reflections: working middle-class women in Egypt / Safia K. Mohsen -- The ringing / Fathiyyah Awada -- Fatima: A history of an Egyptian from Bulaq / Evelyn Early -- Divorce / Leila Abouzeid -- Part III. Health and Education: Continuity and change in women\'s education in the Arab states / Nagat Al-Sanabary -- Growing up female in Egypt (from Mudhakkirat tabiba) / Nawal Al-Sa\'dawi -- Ideology, value changes, and women\'s social position in Libyan society / Mustafa O. Attir -- Women and Public Health in Morocco: One family\'s experience / Donna Lee Bowen -- Women\'s education and its relation to fertility: Report from Baghdad / Ann Bragdon Al-Kadhi -- The social and political implications of female circumcision: The case of Sudan / Nahid F. Toubia -- Part IV. War, Politics and Revolution: Poems / Fadwa Tuqan -- The Kalashnikov Generation / Maroun Baghdadi and Nayla De Freige -- Those memories / Emily Nasrallah -- Encounters with Palestinian women under occupation / Rosemary Sayigh -- The aunt of Rafiq / Daisy Al-Amir -- Part V. Religion and Law: Revitalizing old ideas: Developments in Middle Eastern family law / Eric Mueller -- Recent amendments to Egypt\'s personal status law / Aziza Hussein -- An Islamic activist: Zaynab Al-Ghazali / Valerie J. Hoffmann -- The position of women in Shi\'a Iran: views of the Ulama / Shireen Mahdavi -- Part VI. Work: Women and Work: strategies and choices in a lower-class quarter of Cairo / Andrea B. Rugh -- The shoes / Iqbal Barakah -- Cairo\